#: class-wpforms-epfl-payonline.php:770
msgid "Enable EPFL Payonline payments"
msgstr "Activer les paiements EPFL Payonline"

#: class-wpforms-epfl-payonline.php:781
msgid "EPFL Payonline instance ID"
msgstr "ID de l'instance EPFL Payonline"

#: class-wpforms-epfl-payonline.php:784
msgid ""
"You must create a payment instance (entity that identifies your conference "
"in the Payonline service) by using the \"New Instance\" link in the main "
"menu on <a href=\"https://payonline.epfl.ch\" target=\"_blank\">payonline."
"epfl.ch</a>"
msgstr ""
"Vous devez préalablement créer une instance (entrée qui identifie votre "
"conférence sur Payonline) en utilisant le lien \"Nouvelle Instance\" dans le "
"menu du site <a href=\"https://payonline.epfl.ch\" target=\"_blank"
"\">payonline.epfl.ch</a>"

#: class-wpforms-epfl-payonline.php:792
msgid "WPForms EPFL Payonline Email Address"
msgstr "Email WPForms EPFL Payonline"

#: class-wpforms-epfl-payonline.php:795
msgid "Enter an email address for payments notification"
msgstr "Spécifier une adresse email pour les notifications de paiement."

